//This event listener gets attached every time this button is clicked so to prevent adding the same listener
//multiple times, we are going to remove the listener before re-attaching it. This way we can ensure there is only
//ever 1 instance of the listener on the page. (NOTE: This line will execute without an exception even if the listener doesn't exist yet.)
window.removeEventListener("message", receivePaymentAppMessage);

